	* graph3d.c: Fix old bug which caused 'xzeroaxis' and 'yzeroaxis' to
	mean the opposite of each other in splots.

1999-08-25  Lars Hecking  <lhecking@nmrc.ucc.ie>

	* Makefile.in, makefile.all: Updated.

